Key Match Events: Nikola Jokic recorded a near triple-double with 46 points and 10 rebounds.
Victor Wembanyama had a notable performance with 23 rebounds.
The Denver Nuggets defeated the San Antonio Spurs 122-111 in overtime.
Nikola Jokic outdueled Victor Wembanyama in an OT battle.
Jeremy Sochan threw down a big slam against the Denver Nuggets.
Post-Match Reflections: Nikola Jokic and the Denver Nuggets spoiled Victor Wembanyama's 21st birthday with their victory.
The game was held at Frost Bank Center in San Antonio, TX with an attendance of 19,038.
